<%- include('../partials/header.ejs') %>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar.ejs') %>
    <main style="width:100%;padding:10vh 15vw">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="./assets/students.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Image of student working on the map">
            <div class="card-body" style="padding:3vh 5vw;">
                <h5 class="card-title">Our Project</h5>
                <p class="card-text">With this map project, we want to do a real job as a historian by all investigating
                    our own family as well as a consecrated city. In addition, this project is also the duty of
                    remembrance for all the dead and victims of the war in the Hauts-de-France region.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row" style="padding:2vh 0;">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Local Case Study</h5>
                        <hr>
                        <p class="card-text">In order to carry out this project, each of us chose a town in
                            Hauts-de-France to then carry out a local case study on it.</p>
                        <p class="text-muted">These local case studies are also accessible by scanning the nfc located
                            behind certain city names.</p>
                        <a href="/web/app/resources/local-case-study" class="btn btn-primary">Local Case Study</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
                <div class="card" style="height:100%;">
                    <div class="card-body"
                        style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start;">
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Personal case Study</h5>
                            <hr>
                            <p class="card-text">We have also carried out real work as a historian, in particular with
                                our personal case study where we investigated on our family background.</p>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/web/app/resources/personal-case-study" class="btn btn-primary">Personal Case Study</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>